description: This table logs Ericsson radio access network (RAN) data, including timestamps, cell identifiers, and metadata describing the data schema and version for various data types (e.g., RME capacity usage, auto ESI, and requested RD data).
queries: Show me all schema versions used for RME capacity usage data logged in the last 24 hours.
What is the latest schema version for auto ESI data from cell ID 12345?
Retrieve all timestamps associated with schema version 2.1 for requested RD data.
How many distinct schema versions are present for each data type in the last week?
Find all instances where the schema version for RME capacity usage data is different from the schema version for auto ESI data within the same timestamp.
